lo stars formed show [Fe/H]$>$-2.4 dex. In\nthis case, to explain [$\\alpha$/Fe] data for stars with [Fe/H]$<$-2.4 dex we\nneed stars formed in dSph systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 16:27:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
