he stellar neighbourhood. This result suggests that\nhigh-mass stars and/or stellar clusters containing young massive stars may\ncontinue to accrete for a long time, even after the development of a compact\nHII region.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 20:17:29 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
