s detected in\nthe 4d- or 5d-orbital strongly correlated materials with SOC and in the current\nor near future cold atom systems are presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 20:43:05 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Feb 2017 15:30:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 26 Jul 2020 19:43:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-28"}
