 significantly\ndustier (A$_{H\\alpha}$~1.5-1.6) than those residing in the lowest density\nenvironments (A$_{H\\alpha}$~0.6), deviating significantly from what would be\npredicted given their stellar masses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2016 21:00:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-23"}
