ase the volumetric acquisition of liver tumors in order to evaluate for\ntreatment response. Additional aim is the registration of intraoperative US\nimages via the interactive segmentations to the patient's pre-interventional CT\nacquisitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2016 01:42:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-06-29"}
