ure, at least in a ZnSe-based\nmixed crystal, and not due to any pressure-induced structural transition.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 2 Mar 2016 08:04:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 3 Mar 2016 09:34:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-27"}
